commit.message:
acinclude.m4 (libtool_VERSION): Bump.

2013-11-22  Jonathan Wakely  <jwakely.gcc@gmail.com>

	* acinclude.m4 (libtool_VERSION): Bump.
	* configure: Regenerate.
	* doc/xml/manual/abi.xml: Update version information.

From-SVN: r205258
